{"tid":1006203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然間諗起","createTime":"2019-02-02T18:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T19:05:15.000Z","uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0421f4533ca1d2943a070ed5359d6646418be3","tid":1006203,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:49:34.000Z","msg":"以前細個，以為豚肉，係海豚嘅肉，去日本料理餐廳會唔敢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242103214acfc754e148d86dbf69dba458c330a5","tid":1006203,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:51:02.000Z","msg":"仲有我一直以為，菠蘿皮同榴槤皮一樣咁硬<br />\n直到我前兩日買咗個菠蘿親手切佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147c49d05b57c2f959258f92810d8fbdb341df8f","tid":1006203,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:52:07.000Z","msg":"以前以為係海豚肉 咁高級次次叫<br />\n點知原來係垃圾豬肉"},{"pid":"4bdae9107b66fa214d552923043c0e3c14ffa7b2","tid":1006203,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:54:40.000Z","msg":"下 你地搞錯咗wor 豚肉係海豚肉黎"},{"pid":"ee76f2f3d642db6169149b4146df9f5d16085900","tid":1006203,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:59:36.000Z","msg":"以前細個一直以為，樓下管理處有我屋企後備鎖鑰（喺唔喺咁打？）如果唔記得可以叫佢地開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直到有一次，同細妹偷偷地落去公園玩（嗰陣小學，仲要無著褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前細個成日淨喺落件T加底底喺屋企，嗰陣真係好細個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依加諗返起我都唔知點解可以唔記得著埋條褲先出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）然後呀媽嗰陣去咗買餸，佢無帶鎖鑰，本來諗住我地喺屋企可以開門比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又貪玩帶埋細妹落樓下公園，直到我呀媽返嚟見到我地喺樓下等佢<br />\n<br />\n而等佢嘅期間，我去管理處問個姨姨可唔可以比我地屋企條鎖鑰我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後比佢鬧你都傻嘅我點會有你屋企鎖鑰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰陣我先知原來管理處係無後備鎖鑰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d597ec28bfd0c156456cfe31afdfaf902a704b","tid":1006203,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"147c49d05b57c2f959258f92810d8fbdb341df8f","tid":1006203,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:52:07.000Z","msg":"以前以為係海豚肉 咁高級次次叫<br />\n點知原來係垃圾豬肉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:59:59.000Z","msg":"認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b5db44a809396bf94a2d7dcf61087b564cfa4a","tid":1006203,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4bdae9107b66fa214d552923043c0e3c14ffa7b2","tid":1006203,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:54:40.000Z","msg":"下 你地搞錯咗wor 豚肉係海豚肉黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T19:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6df1d141d98a09e181df19f737634e854d29f96","tid":1006203,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T19:04:35.000Z","msg":"真喺海豚肉黎㗎喎，你地做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc1eadad8f55ca2e49dfb6d770f21fb17468ba1","tid":1006203,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b5db44a809396bf94a2d7dcf61087b564cfa4a","tid":1006203,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4bdae9107b66fa214d552923043c0e3c14ffa7b2","tid":1006203,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-